table.title: Canberra Airport - Total passengers and aircraft movements

query: In the years where forecasts were available, as in 2001–02, 2004–05, 2008–09, and 2014–15, how accurate were the 2003 predictions of total movements and passenger numbers?
summary: In 2003, the predictions for total movements and passenger numbers at Canberra Airport not very accurate when look at years with available forecasts. In 2001-02, the estimated total movements were much too high at 90,281 compared to actual number of 39,716. The passenger prediction for 2002-03 was also too high at 2,176,603 compared to the real 1,916,351 passengers. But, the predictions for 2004-05 and 2014-15 were more close, with guessing 2,280,557 and 3,476,797 passengers, compared to real numbers of 2,478,705 and 2,803,989 passengers.

query: Looking at the office holding periods, who served the longest and shortest terms as the Foreign Minister in the 1800s, and which parties did they represent?
summary: Paul de Favereau has longest time as Foreign Minister in 1800s, from 1896 to 1907, he was in PC (Catholic Party). But is also some ministers has very short time, in 1831 year only, like Sylvain Van de Weyer, Joseph Lebeau, and Felix de Muelenaere. All of they only working for 1831. Van de Weyer and Lebeau is from the LP (Liberal Party) when they work short time, but de Muelenaere is from PC (Catholic Party). Important to talk is Felix de Muelenaere also working at other years, in 1834-1836 and 1843-1845, he is very important person in Foreign Ministers in 1800s.

query: Summarize the basic information of the episodes aired in the 2006 TV Season.
summary: The 2006 TV Season saw the airing of Seasons 2 through 4 of the Amor En Custodia series. All episodes aired Monday through Friday at 9:00 PM EDT, beginning with Season 2's premiere on January 16, and ending with Season 4's finale on January 6 the following year. All seasons held a top spot in the Spanish language rankings, with Season 2 achieving 1st place with 9.4 viewers in millions, while Season 3 earned 1st place again with an increased viewership of 9.9 million people. Lastly, Season 4 achieved a viewership of 9.7 million people for a 2nd place rank in the Spanish language rankings.

query: Summarize the basic information of all finals reached by Dominique Monami on Clay courts.
summary: Dominique Monami reached a total of three finals on Clay courts. In 1996, Monami won the tournament in Cardiff, Great Britain against Laurence Courtois with a score of 6-4 and 6-2. In 1998, Monami was a runner-up at the tournament in Spain against Patty Schnyder with a score of 6-3, 4-6, and 0-6. Finally, in 2000, Monami was a runner-up at the tournament in Belgium against Anna Smashnova with a score of 2-6 and 5-7.
